question to instructor.

42
00:04:07,360  -->  00:04:10,780
2nd, go to stack overflow.

43
00:04:11,140  -->  00:04:16,780
You know, stack overflow is like a global
knowledge for programming questions.

44
00:04:17,500  -->  00:04:21,040
Or you can always google.

45
